10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
11 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 698.3, is
12 amended to read as follows:
13 Section 698.3. A. The State Board of Veterinary Medical
14 Examiners is hereby re-created, to continue until July 1, 2025 2030,
15 in accordance with the provisions of the Oklahoma Sunset Law, to
16 regulate and enforce the practice of veterinary medicine in this
17 state in accordance with the Oklahoma Veterinary Practice Act.
18 B. 1. The duty of determining a person's initial and
19 continuing qualification and fitness for the practice of veterinary
20 medicine, of proceeding against the unlawful and unlicensed practice
21 of veterinary medicine and of enforcing the Oklahoma Veterinary
22 Practice Act is hereby delegated to the Board. That duty shall be
23 discharged in accordance with the Oklahoma Veterinary Practice Act
24 and other applicable statutes.
